          <para styleclass="Notes"><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">Note: </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">When the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Constant-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> segment is one segment of a complete machine-cycle use a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Gearing FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, to replace a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> &#160;- assuming a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Linear-Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> is connected to the input of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Gearing FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">When the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Gearing-Ratio = 1</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> (in the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Gearing dialog</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">), the output equals its input, it increases steadily from 0 to 360.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">If you enter the equation 270/360 as the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Gearing Ratio</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> the output is from 0 to 270, when its input is from 0 to 360.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Thus, you can see it is easy to use a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Gearing FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> to output a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Constant-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> for a complete a machine-cycle. </text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
